om\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/blog-gallery3-768x351.jpg 768w, https:\/\/growhub.themepul.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/blog-gallery3-1536x701.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/growhub.themepul.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/blog-gallery3.jpg 1752w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Focus on building a Minimum Viable Product that addresses the core needs of your target audience. This allows for quick market entry, feedback collection, and iterative improvements based on user responses.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Launching a startup is an exhilarating journey, but the path to success involves more than just a great idea. This guide aims to provide a roadmap for entrepreneurs, offering insights and strategies for not only getting your startup off the ground but also scaling it for sustained growth. \u201cIT IS A LONG FACT THAT A [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":54,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[11,10],"tags":[12,8,5,7],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/growhub.themepul.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/growhub.themepul.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/growhub.themepul.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/growhub.themepul.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/growhub.themepul.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=26"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/growhub.themepul.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/growhub.themepul.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/54"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/growhub.themepul.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=26"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/growhub.theme